  <brief_title>Endothelial Dysfunction in Subjects With History of Premature Coronary Artery Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Placebo-controlled Crossover Trial of Endothelial Function Improvement in Subjects With History of Premature Coronary Artery Disease</official_title>
