  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this prospective study is to investigate the prevalence of endothelial dysfunction
      in subjects with family history of premature coronary heart disease. At the same time, the
      effect of atorvastatin in treating subclinical endothelial dysfunction in those patients will
      be evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
