  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  within 1 year

          -  the siblings of premature coronary heart disease(male&lt;55years old, female&lt;65years old:
             Framingham Heart Study)patients admitted relevant hospital

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Documented coronary heart disease

          -  Any woman of childbearing potential who is pregnant, seeking to become pregnant or
             suspects that she may be pregnant.
